Datatec First-Half Profit More Than Doubles, Plans Two Dividend Payments

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-09-15T06:05:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/datatec-first-half-profit-more-than-doubles-plans-two-dividend-payments.html
Datatec Ltd. (DTC)  said earnings per
share rose to as much as 20 cents in the six months through
August compared with 8.8 cents a year earlier.  The company plans to pay an interim dividend in addition to
a final payout.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
